WEBVTT

00:06:28.200 --> 00:06:31.136
such as self-defense within the home.

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:33.000
Within the home.

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:38.176
This change over time is striking to me,

00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:39.736
because it reminds us

00:06:39.760 --> 00:06:43.056
that the interpretation
of the Second Amendment

00:06:43.080 --> 00:06:45.896
and cultural attitudes about guns

00:06:45.920 --> 00:06:47.640
have changed over time.

00:06:48.880 --> 00:06:52.560
Which gives me hope
they could change again.

00:06:53.040 --> 00:06:57.840
(Applause)